XML-RPC Library With XML-RPC Interface Compiler
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Libxr is a XML-RPC library with support for:

  - SSLv3/TLSv1 using OpenSSL.
  - IPV6 as soon as OpenSSL 0.9.9 is released.
  - Persistent connections over HTTP/1.1
  - Servlet "session" support for non-persistent connections.
  - Multiple RPC transports. (XML-RPC and JSON).
  - XML-RPC interface description language (XDL).
  - XML-RPC client stubs/servlet skels compiler.
  - Multiple servlets per server.
  - Servlet lifetime (init -- call -- call -- fini).
  - Multi-platform (linux, mingw32 on windows).
  - VALA language support for client interface.
